#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:107 14c1001d8e8341ddadcad575a9fceaea
msgid ""
"tuple - A tuple of 11 elements containing detailed touch status:  - ``[0]"
" deltaX`` (int): The X-axis difference since the last measurement. - "
"``[1] deltaY`` (int): The Y-axis difference since the last measurement. -"
" ``[2] distanceX`` (int): The total X-axis distance moved since touched. "
"- ``[3] distanceY`` (int): The total Y-axis distance moved since touched."
" - ``[4] isPressed`` (bool): True if currently being pressed. - ``[5] "
"wasPressed`` (bool): True if just transitioned to pressed state. - ``[6] "
"wasClicked`` (bool): True if just clicked. - ``[7] isReleased`` (bool): "
"True if currently released. - ``[8] wasReleased`` (bool): True if just "
"transitioned to released state. - ``[9] isHolding`` (bool): True if "
"currently being held. - ``[10] wasHold`` (bool): True if it was held."
msgstr "元组 - 一个包含 11 个元素的元组，提供触摸状态的详细信息：``[0] deltaX`` (int)：自上次测量以来在 X 轴上的位移差；``[1] deltaY`` (int)：自上次测量以来在 Y 轴上的位移差；``[2] distanceX`` (int)：自触摸开始以来在 X 轴上的累计移动距离；``[3] distanceY`` (int)：自触摸开始以来在 Y 轴上的累计移动距离；``[4] isPressed`` (bool)：当前是否处于按下状态；``[5] wasPressed`` (bool)：是否刚刚变为按下状态；``[6] wasClicked`` (bool)：是否刚刚完成一次点击；``[7] isReleased`` (bool)：当前是否处于释放状态；``[8] wasReleased`` (bool)：是否刚刚从按下变为释放状态；``[9] isHolding`` (bool)：当前是否处于长按保持状态；``[10] wasHold`` (bool)：是否曾经处于长按保持状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:107 ec60bdc67fe948418140ad1798738ca3
msgid "tuple - A tuple of 11 elements containing detailed touch status:"
msgstr "元组 - 一个包含 11 个元素的元组，提供触摸状态的详细信息："

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:109 26d1c13c04b346a38abe75e81f66a788
msgid "``[0] deltaX`` (int): The X-axis difference since the last measurement."
msgstr "``[0] deltaX`` (int)：自上次测量以来在 X 轴上的位移差。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:110 1805f9bd43e844d2922e7446785a5059
msgid "``[1] deltaY`` (int): The Y-axis difference since the last measurement."
msgstr "``[1] deltaY`` (int)：自上次测量以来在 Y 轴上的位移差。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:111 10a0d867bf9c48ce92bab61ab9cd3ada
msgid "``[2] distanceX`` (int): The total X-axis distance moved since touched."
msgstr "``[2] distanceX`` (int)：自触摸开始以来在 X 轴上的累计移动距离。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:112 693cbbefba3a42dfa8f580fa048fc390
msgid "``[3] distanceY`` (int): The total Y-axis distance moved since touched."
msgstr "``[3] distanceY`` (int)：自触摸开始以来在 Y 轴上的累计移动距离。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:113 299a44535129458d84f12eed417ce9c1
msgid "``[4] isPressed`` (bool): True if currently being pressed."
msgstr "``[4] isPressed`` (bool)：当前是否处于按下状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:114 e8885e6b268f4d84b4d222710db86711
msgid "``[5] wasPressed`` (bool): True if just transitioned to pressed state."
msgstr "``[5] wasPressed`` (bool)：是否刚刚变为按下状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:115 aaf288f73686456dbc52d2cf139b13fc
msgid "``[6] wasClicked`` (bool): True if just clicked."
msgstr "``[6] wasClicked`` (bool)：是否刚刚完成一次点击。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:116 3e621464a0514e9aa500451d3aaf6f30
msgid "``[7] isReleased`` (bool): True if currently released."
msgstr "``[7] isReleased`` (bool)：当前是否处于释放状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:117 6ba39a6a69ee49ceb5c46fb3a20b32d8
msgid "``[8] wasReleased`` (bool): True if just transitioned to released state."
msgstr "``[8] wasReleased`` (bool)：是否刚刚从按下变为释放状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:118 51f462ebcb6e4bf2b01371a169486ca0
msgid "``[9] isHolding`` (bool): True if currently being held."
msgstr "``[9] isHolding`` (bool)：当前是否处于长按保持状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:119 88b40a041c494a01b3ed23b473808e22
msgid "``[10] wasHold`` (bool): True if it was held."
msgstr "``[10] wasHold`` (bool)：是否曾经处于长按保持状态。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:129 4fbb53533cfd47fc8a67e187f0b78584
msgid "Get the raw touch point coordinates."
msgstr "获取原始触点坐标。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:132 216c18d7988d482b9a54cd44b0aa875f
msgid ""
"tuple - A tuple of 4 elements containing raw touch point data:  - ``[0] "
"x`` (int): The raw X coordinate. - ``[1] y`` (int): The raw Y coordinate."
" - ``[2] size`` (int): The size or pressure of the touch point. - ``[3] "
"id`` (int): The unique identifier for tracking the touch point."
msgstr "元组 - 一个包含 4 个元素的元组，提供原始触点数据：``[0] x`` (int)：原始 X 坐标；``[1] y`` (int)：原始 Y 坐标；``[2] size`` (int)：触点的大小或压力；``[3] id`` (int)：用于跟踪该触点的唯一标识。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:132 df69f5dbde2f407e903550bb44478cae
msgid "tuple - A tuple of 4 elements containing raw touch point data:"
msgstr "元组 - 一个包含 4 个元素的元组，提供原始触点数据："

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:134 def12a302b824f229984c9894c8f7dca
msgid "``[0] x`` (int): The raw X coordinate."
msgstr "``[0] x`` (int)：原始 X 坐标。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:135 1a2b2fa41be64dea89797ff83d8e0791
msgid "``[1] y`` (int): The raw Y coordinate."
msgstr "``[1] y`` (int)：原始 Y 坐标。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:136 531c08de693149f9833f747a316c4687
msgid "``[2] size`` (int): The size or pressure of the touch point."
msgstr "``[2] size`` (int)：触点的大小或压力。"

#: ../../source/hardware/touch.rst:137 d606c166358f4ac9b0fee217e993f8c3
msgid "``[3] id`` (int): The unique identifier for tracking the touch point."
msgstr "``[3] id`` (int)：用于跟踪该触点的唯一标识。"

